    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owners. The engine starts up reliably and runs smoothly, while the transmission provides seamless shifts during both city and highway driving. The exterior retains a nice shine with only minor surface wear consistent with careful use, and the interior is clean and free of any major blemishes. It\u2019s a solid, dependable choice for anyone looking for a well-maintained car that is ready for the road.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
