    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable car at an affordable price point. The exterior shows some signs of its history, including several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some thinning paint on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear and some staining consistent with regular use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may soon require routine maintenance or minor repairs to keep it in peak operating form. It is a functional vehicle that offers good value for those who don't mind a bit of character and cosmetic wear.",
      "price": 19500.0,
