    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior luster to the meticulously maintained cabin, adheres to the highest standards of professional care. This unit has undergone an exhaustive diagnostic evaluation to ensure mechanical perfection, offering a driving experience that is indistinguishable from its original state. We invite the most discerning clientele to acquire a vehicle that transcends the standard pre-owned market, standing as a definitive testament to superior engineering and fastidious ownership.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
