    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this 2021 Porsche 718 Cayman is a pristine example of precision engineering. The Chalk exterior remains flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that highlights the car\u2019s aggressive lines without a single stone chip or swirl mark in sight. Inside, the black leather interior retains its factory-fresh aroma; the seat bolsters show zero wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun exposure or blemishes. Mechanically, this vehicle is impeccable, having covered only 4,200 miles and receiving regular maintenance exclusively at authorized dealerships. It has been meticulously garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment, never seen rain, and comes from a smoke-free, pet-free home. All original documentation, both keys, and a clean title are included. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
